## 八、常用优化策略

### 8.1 分帧处理

```typescript
// 将大量计算分到多帧执行
class FrameScheduler {
    private tasks: Array<() => void> = [];
    private maxPerFrame = 10;

    addTask(task: () => void): void {
        this.tasks.push(task);
    }

    update(): void {
        let count = 0;
        while (this.tasks.length > 0 && count < this.maxPerFrame) {
            let task = this.tasks.shift();
            task();
            count++;
        }
    }
}
```

